<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 10:06:46 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>散居海外的犹太人成为以色列行为的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/diaspora-jews-are-hostages-to-israels-behavior/0000018b-e420-d867-abab-f5a4592d0000</link><description>散居海外的犹太人经历了惨痛的教训，无论他们的派别或政治立场如何，他们都会成为严厉批评以色列行为的出气筒，煽动行为会演变成反犹太主义。现在是以色列至少承认这一现实的时候了</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 08:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/diaspora-jews-are-hostages-to-israels-behavior/0000018b-e420-d867-abab-f5a4592d0000</guid></item><item><title>报告称以色列、美国和哈马斯就人质交易已接近达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/negotiations-over-hostage-release-held-up-as-israel-waits-for-hamas/0000018b-e69d-dffa-adef-e69d32ea0000</link><description>然而，其他消息人士称，谈判陷入僵局，因为以色列正在等待知道哈马斯计划释放多少妇女和儿童，然后再决定下一步行动</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 08:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/negotiations-over-hostage-release-held-up-as-israel-waits-for-hamas/0000018b-e69d-dffa-adef-e69d32ea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军和真主党在黎巴嫩发射后进行交火；报告：以色列和哈马斯逐步达成人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-live/biden-says-gaza-and-west-bank-should-be-ruled-by-renewed-pa/0000018b-e568-dffa-adef-e76822250000</link><description>以色列国防军在周六宣布 6 人死亡后，又任命了两名阵亡士兵。 ■ 《华盛顿邮报》：以色列、美国和哈马斯之间的人质协议即将达成协议 ■ 内塔尼亚胡：人道主义援助对于国际支持至关重要 ■ 数千人在特拉维夫集会要求归还人质周六 ■ 加沙医疗消息来源：以色列国防军袭击加沙南部汗尤尼斯的死亡人数上升至 64 人 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙有 239 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 04:01:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-live/biden-says-gaza-and-west-bank-should-be-ruled-by-renewed-pa/0000018b-e568-dffa-adef-e76822250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和世界必须认清反犹太主义者的本质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-world-must-recognize-antisemites-for-what-they-are/0000018b-e3be-d867-abab-f7be96930000</link><description>让我们考虑一下在自诩为人文自由主义者中变得如此流行的口号：从河流到海洋，巴勒斯坦将是自由的。实际上免费什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-world-must-recognize-antisemites-for-what-they-are/0000018b-e3be-d867-abab-f7be96930000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-e4e9-dffa-adef-e6e955bf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-e4e9-dffa-adef-e6e955bf0000</guid></item><item><title>不合时宜：人质交易缺乏紧迫性已达到临界点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/out-of-time-the-lack-of-urgency-for-a-hostage-deal-is-reaching-a-tipping-point/0000018b-e416-dffa-adef-e61656e50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/out-of-time-the-lack-of-urgency-for-a-hostage-deal-is-reaching-a-tipping-point/0000018b-e416-dffa-adef-e61656e50000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列国防军进一步深入加沙，内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁在与哈马斯的人质协议上出现分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-split-over-terms-of-hostage-deal-as-idf-expands-operation/0000018b-e40e-d867-abab-f5ae6e680000</link><description>三个因素将决定战争的成败：释放人质、摧毁地道和消灭哈马斯高级指挥官。另一方坚持认为军方必须继续全力向哈马斯施加压力</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-split-over-terms-of-hostage-deal-as-idf-expands-operation/0000018b-e40e-d867-abab-f5ae6e680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布在加沙战斗中丧生的八名士兵的姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-names-of-five-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-e480-d867-abab-f5a46bfc0000</link><description>迄今为止，以色列国防军已公布自10月7日与哈马斯开战以来阵亡的380名士兵的姓名</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 23:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-names-of-five-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-e480-d867-abab-f5a46bfc0000</guid></item><item><title>罗杰·沃特斯：停止否认 10 月 7 日哈马斯暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/an-open-letter-to-roger-waters/0000018b-e3be-d168-a3ef-f7fe96410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 22:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/an-open-letter-to-roger-waters/0000018b-e3be-d168-a3ef-f7fe96410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将一名在约旦河西岸清真寺投掷眩晕手榴弹的士兵停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-soldier-seen-throwing-stun-grenade-at-west-bank-mosque/0000018b-e450-df9a-ab8b-fed84d250000</link><description>该事件发生之际，美国政府敦促以色列打击约旦河西岸的极端主义活动。 ■ 以色列国防军发言人：“这是一起违反以色列国防军价值观的严重事件”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 22:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-soldier-seen-throwing-stun-grenade-at-west-bank-mosque/0000018b-e450-df9a-ab8b-fed84d250000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示，美国准备对袭击约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的以色列“极端分子”实施签证禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/u-s-to-issue-visa-bans-on-israeli-extremists-attacking-palestinians-in-west-bank/0000018b-e409-df9a-ab8b-fec973190000</link><description>拜登总统在《华盛顿邮报》专栏文章中透露，此举是其政府自上台以来对以色列采取的最重大的惩罚措施</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 20:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/u-s-to-issue-visa-bans-on-israeli-extremists-attacking-palestinians-in-west-bank/0000018b-e409-df9a-ab8b-fec973190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部阿拉伯城市25岁男子被枪杀，警方逮捕嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/25-year-old-shot-dead-in-northern-israeli-arab-city-police-arrest-suspect/0000018b-e3fa-d867-abab-f7fec22a0000</link><description>此次枪击事件使年初以来以色列阿拉伯社会的谋杀案数量达到210起，标志着自与哈马斯开战以来以色列阿拉伯人的谋杀案数量大幅减少</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 20:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/25-year-old-shot-dead-in-northern-israeli-arab-city-police-arrest-suspect/0000018b-e3fa-d867-abab-f7fec22a0000</guid></item><item><title>惊慌失措的人们离开希法医院，据报道加沙北部学校有数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/panicked-people-leave-shifa-hospital-while-dozens-reportedly-killed-at-north-gaza-school/0000018b-e3d5-df9a-ab8b-ffdd46250000</link><description>撤离后只剩下以色列军队和骨干人员来照顾那些病重而无法移动的人。以色列表示，加沙北部的医院是其旨在镇压哈马斯的地面攻势的主要目标，声称这些医院被用作激进分子的指挥中心和武器库</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 19:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/panicked-people-leave-shifa-hospital-while-dozens-reportedly-killed-at-north-gaza-school/0000018b-e3d5-df9a-ab8b-ffdd46250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对派领导人拉皮德试图争取利库德集团成员的支持以推翻内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-trying-to-muster-support-from-likud-mks-to-topple-netanyahu/0000018b-e391-dffa-adef-e791daee0000</link><description>Yesh Atid 主席 Yair Lapid 希望在不信任投票中获得足够的支持，并与利库德集团等议员进行了交谈。然而，许多MKs可能会拒绝依赖阿拉伯政党，而他的反对党伙伴本尼·甘茨(Benny Gantz)在选举民意调查中有支持，他更愿意提前举行选举</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 19:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-trying-to-muster-support-from-likud-mks-to-topple-netanyahu/0000018b-e391-dffa-adef-e791daee0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属游行抵达耶路撒冷，在内塔尼亚胡总理办公室前集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-march-reaches-jerusalem-rally-in-front-of-pm-netanyahus-office/0000018b-e326-d867-abab-f7a628140000</link><description>大约一万名游行者进入首都，随后将在特拉维夫举行另一场集会。这些家人稍后将会见以色列战时内阁的三名成员，而总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡尚未接受他们的邀请</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 16:31:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-march-reaches-jerusalem-rally-in-front-of-pm-netanyahus-office/0000018b-e326-d867-abab-f7a628140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全机构：哈马斯可能事先不了解新星节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-establishment-hamas-likely-didnt-have-prior-knowledge-of-nova-festival/0000018b-e2ee-d168-a3ef-f7fe8ca20000</link><description>以色列高级安全官员估计，哈马斯通过无人机或降落伞飞行者发现了诺瓦音乐节，并利用其通讯系统将恐怖分子引导至该地点</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-establishment-hamas-likely-didnt-have-prior-knowledge-of-nova-festival/0000018b-e2ee-d168-a3ef-f7fe8ca20000</guid></item><item><title>数百名布兰代斯校友威胁要停止捐款，除非亲巴勒斯坦组织恢复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-alumni-threaten-to-stop-donations-unless-pro-palestinian-group-reinstated/0000018b-e2f0-df9a-ab8b-fef86a7a0000</link><description>在写给布兰代斯大学校长的一封信中，校友们表示，除非学校收回有效禁止巴勒斯坦正义学生组织在校园内举办活动的决定，否则他们将撤回资助。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:24:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-alumni-threaten-to-stop-donations-unless-pro-palestinian-group-reinstated/0000018b-e2f0-df9a-ab8b-fef86a7a0000</guid></item><item><title>马斯克：“非殖民化”、“从河流到海洋”等术语将导致X暂停</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/musk-decolonization-and-from-the-river-to-the-sea-will-result-in-suspension-from-x/0000018b-e2ce-dffa-adef-e6ce41b40000</link><description>在一些全球最大的公司暂停了该平台上的广告后，马斯克写道：“明确呼吁极端暴力违反了我们的服务条款，并将导致我们的服务被暂停。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:16:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/musk-decolonization-and-from-the-river-to-the-sea-will-result-in-suspension-from-x/0000018b-e2ce-dffa-adef-e6ce41b40000</guid></item><item><title>坦桑尼亚宣布一名被哈马斯绑架到加沙的坦桑尼亚公民死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/tanzania-announces-death-of-one-of-its-citizens-kidnapped-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-e24b-d168-a3ef-f7fb6b530000</link><description>22 岁的克莱门斯·费利克斯·马坦加 (Clemence Felix Matanga) 显然于 10 月 7 日在尼尔奥兹基布兹 (Kibbutz Nir ​​Oz) 被劫为人质。然而，目前尚不清楚他的死亡是如何得到确认的，也不清楚他的尸体是否已被找到</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 14:51:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/tanzania-announces-death-of-one-of-its-citizens-kidnapped-by-hamas-in-gaza/0000018b-e24b-d168-a3ef-f7fb6b530000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军杀死五名约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人，称这是计划中的迫在眉睫的恐怖袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-five-west-bank-palestinians-it-says-planned-terror-attack/0000018b-e17c-dffa-adef-e77c09630000</link><description>以色列军队袭击了纳布卢斯附近巴拉塔难民营内用作法塔赫运动总部的设施。巴勒斯坦人报告称，伤亡者中有一名 14 岁男孩</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 11:01:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/idf-kills-five-west-bank-palestinians-it-says-planned-terror-attack/0000018b-e17c-dffa-adef-e77c09630000</guid></item></channel></rss>